## D25 Wiki Knowledge Layer — Storage, Tree API, Raw Resources, and Agent Tools
**Status:** done
**Tags:** stack:both, module:wiki
**Depends on:** G18, A10

### Data Model

```rust
struct WikiPage {
    slug: String,            // path-based: "guide/getting-started"
    title: String,
    content: String,         // markdown content
    source_type: WikiSource,  // Manual, Guide, ApiRef, Custom
    tags: Vec<String>,
    version: u32,
    created_at: u64,
    updated_at: u64,
}

struct TreeNode {
    name: String,
    path: String,            // relative path from wiki/ or raw/ root
    node_type: String,       // "file" | "folder"
    children: Option<Vec<TreeNode>>,
    size: Option<u64>,
    modified: Option<u64>,
}

enum WikiSource { Manual, Guide, ApiRef, Custom }
```

### Storage Layout

```
{project}/
├── specs/          # existing specs
├── wiki/
│   ├── _manifest.json    # page metadata index
│   ├── guide/
│   │   ├── getting-started.md
│   │   └── advanced/
│   │       └── api-reference.md
│   └── readme.md
└── raw/
    ├── datasheets/
    │   ├── stm32f4-datasheet.pdf
    │   └── pinout.png
    └── meeting-notes/
        └── 2024-01-15.md
```

### API Endpoints

| Endpoint | Method | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `/api/forge/wiki/{project}/tree` | GET | Wiki directory tree (TreeNode[]) |
| `/api/forge/wiki/{project}/pages` | GET/POST | List/Create wiki pages |
| `/api/forge/wiki/{project}/page/{*slug}` | GET/PUT/DELETE | Read/Update/Delete wiki page (path-based) |
| `/api/forge/wiki/{project}/search` | POST | Full-text search |
| `/api/forge/raw/{project}/tree` | GET | Raw directory tree |
| `/api/forge/raw/{project}/upload` | POST | Multipart file upload (50MB limit) |
| `/api/forge/raw/{project}/file/{*path}` | GET/DELETE | Serve/Delete raw file |
| `/api/forge/raw/{project}/mkdir` | POST | Create raw subdirectory |

### Agent Tools

| Tool | Description | Profession Access |
|---|---|---|
| `query_wiki` | Full-text search (semantic RAG planned) | All professions |
| `create_wiki_page` | Create page with path-based slug | Coder, Documenter |
| `update_wiki_page` | Update page content with versioning | Coder, Documenter |
| `list_wiki` | List all wiki pages with metadata | All professions |

