## D35 GoalsTable Tree View Component
**Status:** implemented
**Module:** `frontend/src/components/category/GoalsTable.vue`
**Tags:** stack:frontend, module:specs
**Depends on:** G21, D10

### Structure

```vue
<!-- GoalsTable.vue -->
<div class="goals-tree">
  <div
    v-for="row in treeRows"
    :key="row.item.id"
    class="goal-node"
    :class="{ 'is-root': row.level === 0, 'is-sub': row.level > 0 }"
    @click="onRowClick(row.item)"
  >
    <!-- Indent spacer (level × 1.25rem) -->
    <div class="node-indent" :style="{ width: row.level * 1.25 + 'rem' }"></div>

    <!-- Toggle area: only rendered when row.hasChildren -->
    <div
      v-if="row.hasChildren"
      class="node-toggle-area"
      :class="{ expanded: treeExpanded.has(row.item.id) }"
      @click.stop="toggleTree(row.item.id)"
    >
      <span v-if="row.childCount > 0" class="node-children-count">
        {{ row.childCount }}
      </span>
      <span class="node-chevron"><ChevronRight :size="14" /></span>
    </div>

    <!-- Left column: ID -->
    <div class="node-left"><span class="node-id">{{ row.item.id }}</span></div>

    <!-- Right column: title + meta -->
    <div class="node-right">
      <span class="node-title">{{ row.item.title }}</span>
      <span v-if="row.item.priority" class="node-priority">{{ row.item.priority }}</span>
      <StatusBadge :status="row.item.status" size="sm" />
      <span v-if="row.item.tags?.length" class="node-tags">
        <span
          v-for="tag in item.tags.slice(0, 2)"
          :key="tag"
          class="tag-chip"
          :class="parseTag(tag).type"
          :title="parseTag(tag).full"
        >{{ parseTag(tag).value }}</span>
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
```

### Key Behaviors

| Behavior | Implementation |
|---|---|
| Row click | Opens `GoalDetailModal` via `@open-detail` emit |
| Toggle click | `stopPropagation` + `toggleTree(id)`; only when `hasChildren` |
| Leaf goals | No toggle area rendered; entire row is clickable |
| Sub-goals | Indented via `.node-indent`; no toggle area |
| Expansion | `treeExpanded: Set<string>` controls visibility; `treeRows` recomputed |

### Styling

- `.goal-node`: `display: flex; align-items: stretch; min-height: 44px`
- `.node-toggle-area`: `width: 2.5rem; align-self: stretch; cursor: pointer`
- `.node-left`: fixed left column with `padding-left: 1rem`
- `.node-right`: `flex: 1` with title ellipsis truncation

